{"tid":2188383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民安隊長官被指駿洋邨當值期間向女隊員「上下其手」 警列非禮案","createTime":"2020-09-04T08:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T08:28:14.000Z","uid":236891,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"961a15395fab14bce494cf5bb7ff00a183642c17","tid":2188383,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:06:25.000Z","msg":"正用作檢疫中心的火炭駿洋邨，近日傳出有人員涉及懷疑性醜聞。網上有帖文指稱，上周一名民安隊男長官在駿洋邨當通宵更期間，曾命令一名女隊員到休息室，藉詞按摩非禮該女隊員達兩小時。民安處未有回應指控，僅指事件已交由警方處理，不會作出任何評論。警方確認接獲報案，暫列非禮案處理，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁「公務員 Secrets 二代」早前轉載一則帖文，提及民安隊一名屬後援部隊的男長官於上周凌晨時分，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>命令一名年輕女隊員到休息室休息，該男長官隨後亦進入該休息室。帖文指，該男長官先獲取女隊員信任，藉詞用手為該女隊員按摩，再對她「上下其手」，持續觸摸女隊員多個私人部位長達近兩小時。</strong></span><br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/UI4VASKJ4BG4RDN6PC5KE3RRKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FUI4VASKJ4BG4RDN6PC5KE3RRKY%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=97317bce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FUI4VASKJ4BG4RDN6PC5KE3RRKY%2F&h=d55140c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/UI4VASKJ4BG4RDN6PC5KE3RRKY/</a><br />\n剩番自己入link睇<br />\n<br />\n成兩個小時冇反抗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160702426cb129fa79ce8e7f3c2cce7a9619451d","tid":2188383,"uid":175208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:07:59.000Z","msg":"分"},{"pid":"73e312debb3dd859fda583b1e365132e1ce9aa43","tid":2188383,"uid":77717,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"狗乸本身都係淫賤水炮車，明顯係勞資糾紛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e522a185ed50c0c108ad5e46d1f87dcc44bf723","tid":2188383,"uid":222970,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"共享天使，差佬食完之後比民安隊"},{"pid":"ed8370400deda4